title: Danish-Korean  post-rock experimentalists Meejah join us Live on KEXP. Watch today 📺

description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Meejah performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded February 09, 2024.

Songs:
Lysgænger (Wind)
Jing (Thunder)
Queen Min, Rise (Fire)
Kwan Yin (Water)
3rd Euljiro (Earth)

Mai Soon Young Øvlisen - Vocals, Guitar, Amp
Andreas Isbrandt Løvenskjold - Lead Guitar, Amp
Daniel Nayberg - Laptop, Ableton Push,  Effects
Asger Lake - Bass, Amp
Emil Lake - Drums

Host: Morgan
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs, Julian Martlew
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Jonathan Jacobson, Luke Knecht
Editor: Carlos Cruz
